{
    "form": {
        "sections": [
            {
                "title": "Customer Personal Details",
                "fields": [
                    {
                        "label": "Title",
                        "type": "select",
                        "options": [
                            "Mr",
                            "Mrs",
                            "Miss"
                        ],
                        "required": true
                    },
                    {
                        "label": "Surname",
                        "type": "text",
                        "required": true
                    },
                    {
                        "label": "First Name",
                        "type": "text",
                        "required": true
                    },
                    {
                        "label": "Gender",
                        "type": "radio",
                        "options": [
                            "Male",
                            "Female"
                        ],
                        "required": true,
                        "onChange": {
                            "action": "updateNextOfKin",
                            "dependency": "Marital Status",
                            "values": {
                                "Married": {
                                    "Male": "WIFE",
                                    "Female": "HUSBAND"
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    },
                    {
                        "label": "Date of Birth",
                        "type": "date",
                        "required": true
                    },
                    {
                        "label": "Marital Status",
                        "type": "select",
                        "options": [
                            "Single",
                            "Married",
                            "Divorced",
                            "Widowed"
                        ],
                        "required": true,
                        "onChange": {
                            "action": "updateNextOfKinSection",
                            "values": {
                                "Married": "showSpousePlusOne",
                                "default": "showTwoNextOfKin"
                            }
                        }
                    },
                    {
                        "label": "Nationality",
                        "type": "text",
                        "default": "Zimbabwean",
                        "required": true
                    },
                    {
                        "label": "ID Number",
                        "type": "text",
                        "required": true
                    },
                    {
                        "label": "Cell Number",
                        "type": "text",
                        "required": true
                    },
                    {
                        "label": "WhatsApp",
                        "type": "text",
                        "required": false
                    },
                    {
                        "label": "Email Address",
                        "type": "email",
                        "required": true
                    },
                    {
                        "label": "Name of Responsible Ministry",
                        "type": "select",
                        "options": [
                            "Ministry of Primary and Secondary Education",
                            "Ministry of Higher and Tertiary Education, Innovation, Science and Technology Development",
                            "Ministry of Health and Child Care",
                            "Ministry of Justice, Legal and Parliamentary Affairs",
                            "Ministry of Defence",
                            "Ministry of Energy and Power Development",
                            "Ministry of Environment, Climate, Tourism and Hospitality Industry",
                            "Ministry of Finance and Economic Development",
                            "Ministry of Foreign Affairs and International Trade",
                            "Ministry of Home Affairs and Cultural Heritage",
                            "Ministry of Industry and Commerce",
                            "Ministry of Information Communication Technology and Courier Services",
                            "Ministry of Information, Publicity and Broadcasting Services",
                            "Ministry of Lands, Agriculture, Fisheries, Water, and Rural Development",
                            "Ministry of Local Government and Public Works",
                            "Ministry of Mines and Mining Development",
                            "Ministry of National Housing and Social Amenities",
                            "Ministry of Public Service, Labour and Social Welfare",
                            "Ministry of Skills Audit and Development",
                            "Ministry of Transport and Infrastructural Development",
                            "Ministry of Women Affairs, Community, Small and Medium Enterprises Development",
                            "Ministry of Youth, Sport, Arts and Recreation"
                        ],
                        "required": true
                    },
                    {
                        "label": "Name of Employer",
                        "type": "text",
                        "required": true
                    },
                    {
                        "label": "Employer Address",
                        "type": "textarea",
                        "required": true
                    },
                    {
                        "label": "Permanent Address",
                        "type": "textarea",
                        "required": true
                    },
                    {
                        "label": "Property Ownership",
                        "type": "radio",
                        "options": [
                            "Owned",
                            "Employer Owned",
                            "Rented",
                            "Mortgaged",
                            "Parents Owned"
                        ],
                        "required": true
                    },
                    {
                        "label": "Period at Current Address",
                        "type": "select",
                        "options": [
                            "Less than One Year",
                            "Between 1â€“2 years",
                            "Between 2-5 years",
                            "More than 5 years"
                        ],
                        "required": true
                    },
                    {
                        "label": "Employment Status",
                        "type": "radio",
                        "options": [
                            "Permanent",
                            "Contract",
                            "Part-time"
                        ],
                        "required": true
                    },
                    {
                        "label": "Job Title",
                        "type": "select",
                        "options": [
                            "Accountant",
                            "Administrator",
                            "Architect",
                            "Artist",
                            "Attorney/Lawyer",
                            "Banker",
                            "Business Owner",
                            "Chef",
                            "Consultant",
                            "Doctor",
                            "Engineer",
                            "Farmer",
                            "Healthcare Professional",
                            "IT Professional",
                            "Manager",
                            "Marketing Professional",
                            "Nurse",
                            "Pharmacist",
                            "Professor/Teacher",
                            "Retired",
                            "Sales Professional",
                            "Self-employed",
                            "Student",
                            "Technician",
                            "Unemployed",
                            "Other"
                        ],
                        "required": true
                    },
                    {
                        "label": "Date of Employment",
                        "type": "date",
                        "required": true
                    },
                    {
                        "label": "Name of Immediate Supervisor",
                        "type": "text",
                        "required": true
                    },
                    {
                        "label": "Cell No of Immediate Supervisor",
                        "type": "text",
                        "required": true
                    },
                    {
                        "label": "Current Net Salary (USD)",
                        "type": "number",
                        "required": true
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "title": "Spouse and Next of Kin Details",
                "id": "nextOfKinSection",
                "dynamicSection": true,
                "variants": {
                    "showSpousePlusOne": {
                        "fields": [
                            {
                                "label": "Spouse's Full Name",
                                "type": "text",
                                "required": true
                            },
                            {
                                "label": "Relationship",
                                "type": "text",
                                "required": true,
                                "value": "",
                                "readOnly": true,
                                "bindTo": "spouseRelationship"
                            },
                            {
                                "label": "Phone Numbers",
                                "type": "text",
                                "required": true
                            },
                            {
                                "label": "Residential Address",
                                "type": "textarea",
                                "required": true
                            },
                            {
                                "label": "Additional Next of Kin Details",
                                "type": "subtitle"
                            },
                            {
                                "label": "Full Name",
                                "type": "text",
                                "required": true
                            },
                            {
                                "label": "Relationship",
                                "type": "text",
                                "required": true
                            },
                            {
                                "label": "Phone Numbers",
                                "type": "text",
                                "required": true
                            },
                            {
                                "label": "Residential Address",
                                "type": "textarea",
                                "required": true
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    "showTwoNextOfKin": {
                        "fields": [
                            {
                                "label": "Next of Kin 1",
                                "type": "subtitle"
                            },
                            {
                                "label": "Full Name",
                                "type": "text",
                                "required": true
                            },
                            {
                                "label": "Relationship",
                                "type": "text",
                                "required": true
                            },
                            {
                                "label": "Phone Numbers",
                                "type": "text",
                                "required": true
                            },
                            {
                                "label": "Residential Address",
                                "type": "textarea",
                                "required": true
                            },
                            {
                                "label": "Next of Kin 2",
                                "type": "subtitle"
                            },
                            {
                                "label": "Full Name",
                                "type": "text",
                                "required": true
                            },
                            {
                                "label": "Relationship",
                                "type": "text",
                                "required": true
                            },
                            {
                                "label": "Phone Numbers",
                                "type": "text",
                                "required": true
                            },
                            {
                                "label": "Residential Address",
                                "type": "textarea",
                                "required": true
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                }
            },
            {
                "title": "Credit Facility Application Details",
                "fields": [
                    {
                        "label": "Installment Amount (USD)",
                        "type": "number",
                        "required": true,
                        "readOnly": true,
                        "bindTo": "productInstallment"
                    },
                    {
                        "label": "Loan Duration",
                        "type": "radio",
                        "options": [
                            "3 months",
                            "6 months",
                            "9 months",
                            "12 months",
                            "Other"
                        ],
                        "required": true,
                        "readOnly": true,
                        "bindTo": "productLoanPeriod"
                    },
                    {
                        "label": "Start Date",
                        "type": "date",
                        "required": true,
                        "readOnly": true,
                        "bindTo": "autoLoanStartDate"
                    },
                    {
                        "label": "End Date",
                        "type": "date",
                        "required": true,
                        "readOnly": true,
                        "bindTo": "autoLoanEndDate"
                    },
                    {
                        "label": "Purpose/Asset Applied For",
                        "type": "textarea",
                        "required": true,
                        "bindTo": "productDescription"
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "title": "Deduction Order Form",
                "fields": [
                    {
                        "label": "First Name",
                        "type": "text",
                        "required": true,
                        "bindTo": "customerFirstName"
                    },
                    {
                        "label": "Surname",
                        "type": "text",
                        "required": true,
                        "bindTo": "customerSurname"
                    },
                    {
                        "label": "ID Number",
                        "type": "text",
                        "required": true,
                        "bindTo": "customerIdNumber"
                    },
                    {
                        "label": "Ministry",
                        "type": "text",
                        "required": true,
                        "bindTo": "customerMinistry"
                    },
                    {
                        "label": "Province",
                        "type": "select",
                        "options": [
                            "Manicaland",
                            "Mashonaland Central",
                            "Mashonaland East",
                            "Mashonaland West",
                            "Masvingo",
                            "Matabeleland North",
                            "Matabeleland South",
                            "Midlands",
                            "Bulawayo",
                            "Harare"
                        ],
                        "required": true
                    },
                    {
                        "label": "Bank Branch",
                        "type": "component",
                        "component": "BranchLocator",
                        "required": true
                    },
                    {
                        "label": "Employee Code Number",
                        "type": "text",
                        "required": true
                    },
                    {
                        "label": "Check Letter",
                        "type": "text",
                        "required": false
                    },
                    {
                        "label": "Department Code (As it appears on your pay slip)",
                        "type": "text",
                        "required": true
                    },
                    {
                        "label": "Station Code (As it appears on your pay slip)",
                        "type": "text",
                        "required": true
                    },
                    {
                        "label": "Monthly Rate (Installment Amount)",
                        "type": "number",
                        "required": true,
                        "bindTo": "productInstallment"
                    },
                    {
                        "label": "From Date",
                        "type": "text",
                        "required": true,
                        "readOnly": true,
                        "bindTo": "autoLoanStartDateText"
                    },
                    {
                        "label": "To Date",
                        "type": "text",
                        "required": true,
                        "readOnly": true,
                        "bindTo": "autoLoanEndDateText"
                    },
                    {
                        "label": "Do you agree with these terms",
                        "type": "radio",
                        "options": [
                            "Yes",
                            "No"
                        ],
                        "required": true,
                        "onChange": {
                            "action": "confirmProceed",
                            "values": {
                                "No": "showConfirmation"
                            }
                        }
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "title": "KYC Documents",
                "fields": [
                    {
                        "label": "National ID (Front & Back)",
                        "type": "file",
                        "accept": "image/*,.pdf",
                        "required": true
                    },
                    {
                        "label": "Latest Payslip",
                        "type": "file",
                        "accept": "image/*,.pdf",
                        "required": true
                    },
                    {
                        "label": "Take Selfie Selfie",
                        "type": "file",
                        "accept": "image/*,.pdf",
                        "required": true
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "title": "Declaration",
                "fields": [
                    {
                        "label": "Full Name",
                        "type": "text",
                        "required": true,
                        "bindTo": "customerFullName"
                    },
                    {
                        "label": "Legal Declaration",
                        "type": "fieldset",
                        "legend": "Binding Legal Declaration",
                        "children": [
                            {
                                "label": "",
                                "type": "html",
                                "html": "<div style='text-align: justify; font-size: 14px;'><p>I, the undersigned applicant, hereby declare and affirm that all information provided in this digital loan application is true, accurate, and complete to the best of my knowledge and belief.</p><p>I understand that providing false information constitutes fraud, which may result in criminal prosecution under Section 136 of the Criminal Law (Codification and Reform) Act [Chapter 9:23] of Zimbabwe, and similar provisions under the Fraud Act 2006 (UK).</p><p>I acknowledge that this electronic submission constitutes a valid and binding legal agreement in accordance with the Electronic Communications and Transactions Act 25 of 2002 (South Africa), specifically Section 22 which provides that agreements concluded electronically are legally enforceable; the Electronic Signatures Regulations 2002 (UK); the E-SIGN Act, 15 U.S.C. Â§ 7001 (US); and Regulation (EU) No 910/2014 (eIDAS Regulation).</p><p>I understand that clicking the checkbox below constitutes an electronic signature as defined in Section 13 of the Electronic Transactions and Electronic Commerce Act (Zimbabwe), Section 7 of the Electronic Communications and Transactions Act (South Africa), Section 7 of the Electronic Communications Act 2000 (UK), and 15 U.S.C. Â§ 7006(5) (US).</p><p>I consent to the collection and processing of my personal information in accordance with applicable data protection legislation including the Data Protection Act (Zimbabwe), POPIA (South Africa), GDPR (EU), and the Data Protection Act 2018 (UK).</p><p>I understand that digital records of this transaction are admissible as evidence under relevant civil evidence legislation in case of legal proceedings.</p></div>"
                            },
                            {
                                "label": "I confirm that I have read, understood, and agree to be bound by this declaration, and I acknowledge that my electronic signature shall have the same legal effect, validity, and enforceability as a manually executed signature",
                                "type": "checkbox",
                                "required": true
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            }
        ]
    }
}
